      <title>比尔·盖茨支持的沙特阿拉伯疾病控制工作使朝觐者的健康得到改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/hajj-pilgrims-get-health-boost-in-gates-supported-disease-effort-in-saudi-arabia</link>
